creator: christian.tremel@itsv.at
text:
httpd and latest lua compiled from source with ibm xlc compiler.

httpd: Syntax error on line 118 of /tmp/apachetest/conf/httpd.conf: Cannot load modules/mod_lua.so into server: rtld: 0712-001 Symbol luaL_optint was referenced\n      from module /tmp/apachetest/modules/mod_lua.so(), but a runtime definition\n\t    of the symbol was not found.\nrtld: 0712-001 Symbol lua_objlen was referenced\n      from module /tmp/apachetest/modules/mod_lua.so(), but a runtime definition\n\t    of the symbol was not found.\nrtld: 0712-001 Symbol luaL_register was referenced\n      from module /tmp/apachetest/modules/mod_lua.so(), but a runtime definition\n\t    of the symbol was not found.\nrtld: 0712-001 Symbol lua_strlen was referenced\n      from module /tmp/apachetest/modules/mod_lua.so(), but a runtime definition\n\t    of the symbol was not found.\nrtld: 0712-002 fatal error: exiting.

all other modules are loading fine.
